lead_paragraph: Wales manager Chris Coleman said players of Gareth Bale's calibre are driven by a desire to achieve success on the grandest stage of the world football and not the financial aspects of the game.

headline.print_headline: Wales Manager Coleman Says Success Drives Bale Not Money
headline.main: Wales Manager Coleman Says Success Drives Bale Not Money
